# Info

Invoked after all recipes have been loaded and processed. This is useful for inspecting the final recipe state or performing post-processing.

# Available Event Fields

- `event.server` - The Minecraft server instance
- Access to recipe information through the server's recipe manager

# Example

```js
ServerEvents.afterRecipes(event => {
	console.log('All recipes have been loaded!')
	
	// Log recipe counts or perform analysis
})
```
